HEADWORD: Ex libris
<hw>Ex` li"bris</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L. <ets>ex</ets> from +
<ets>libris</ets> books.]</ety> <def>An inscription, label, or the like,
in a book indicating its ownership; esp., a bookplate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

